<h1>Welcome to the Magical World of Unicorns!</h1>

<p>Unicorns are legendary creatures often depicted as beautiful horses with a single spiraling horn on their forehead. They symbolize purity, grace, and magic.</p>

<h2>Interesting Facts:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Unicorns are mythical creatures found in various cultures around the world.</li>
  <li>In Western mythology, they are often associated with innocence and enchantment.</li>
  <li>Many stories describe unicorns as gentle, shy, and elusive animals.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Fun Things to Do:</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Draw your own unicorns and imagine their magical worlds.</li>
  <li>Write your own stories about unicorn adventures.</li>
  <li>Learn about how unicorns are used in art and literature.</li>
</ul>

<p>Thanks for visiting our unicorn wonderland! Stay magical!</p>
